LEGEND:
| b(#) Bend To Fret        | b+   Sustained Bend
| r    Release Bend        | qb   Quarter Bend
| h    Hammer On           | p    Pull Off
| ^    Short Vibrato       | ^^   Long Vibrato
| /    Slide Up            | \    Slide Down
|(PH)  Pinch Harmonic      |(AH)  Artificial Harmonic
| x    Fret Hand Mute      | PM   Palm Mute
* Use tip of pick hand index finger for this pinch harmonic